title: "llm-wiki-colab: an llm-wiki durable-memory plugin"
abstract: "A Claude Code (and later Cursor) plugin that packages the llm-wiki durable-memory pattern as installable, opt-in tooling: per-repo wiki memory, SessionStart orientation, verification/discipline gates, a knowledge-graph build, multi-writer push, and federated ask."
